# Dev ↔ Review Checklist

- [ ] EN/FR keys added and used; no hard-coded text in components.
- [ ] Keyboard navigation verified; focus visible; screen-reader labels present.
- [ ] `prefers-reduced-motion` respected; heavy effects gated.
- [ ] Images optimized; critical hero image only is `priority`/eager.
- [ ] Heavy components dynamically imported; no unnecessary client boundaries.
- [ ] Section visuals align with brand: subtle glow, mint accents, consistent spacing.
- [ ] Lighthouse ≥ 90 Perf/A11y on changed pages; no major CLS.
- [ ] Types clear; props well-defined; no unused exports/imports.
- [ ] Tests or storybook examples updated if applicable.
